Name: Average time for Accepted + Assigned across all process variants where it occurs
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Assigned and the end of the case

Name: Total time spent in Accepted + Assigned when followed by Completed + In Call
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Minimum time for Accepted + Assigned in variants that include Completed + In Call
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Assigned and the end of the case

Name: Average duration of Accepted + Assigned compared to the duration of Completed + In Call within the same case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Time from Accepted + Assigned to Completed + In Call in variants where both activities occur consecutively or non-consecutively
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Elapsed time between Accepted + Assigned and the next occurrence of Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average time for Accepted + Assigned in variants that do not contain Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call does not occur

Name: Total time for Accepted + Assigned grouped by country
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country

Name: Time of Accepted + Assigned when it appears after Queued + Awaiting Assignment and before Completed + Resolved
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Cycle Time of Accepted + Assigned in cases that eventually reach Completed + Closed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average time between Accepted + Assigned and Completed + Resolved in variants also containing Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Minimum time for Accepted + Assigned when followed directly by Accepted + In Progress
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Total duration of Accepted + Assigned across high-frequency variants (frequency > 100) versus low-frequency variants (frequency â‰¤ 100)
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Assigned and the end of the case

Name: Time from case start until Accepted + Assigned is performed in cases that later include Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Average time it takes Accepted + Assigned to be executed after Queued + Awaiting Assignment in variants involving Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'
